119
00:06:03,460 --> 00:06:04,550
But I didn't have any drinking buddy.

120
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,070
It was so boring.

121
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,930
So I took the wine

122
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:11,220
