191
00:08:39,570 --> 00:08:40,730
I'll release them immediately.

192
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:43,720
Minister Lu,

193
00:08:43,909 --> 00:08:45,540
I was afraid that

194
00:08:45,710 --> 00:08:48,380
